	The promoter has not provided any No Objection Certificate (NOC) from the bank. Consequently, in the Encumbrance Certificate, we have indicated 'Created' as no supporting documents have been submitted by the promoter. The promoter has stated that the secured loans taken from the bank have been repaid, and hence, there is no requirement for an NOC from the bank. As no NOC was provided, we have not altered the encumbrance status. 
	Additionally, no registered agreements for sale have been provided by the promoter. Therefore, no details related to registered agreements have been filled in this certificate. 
	The promoter has stated that direct sale deeds have been executed at the request of the customers. 
	In certain cases, at the request of customers, plots have been sold directly. Consequently, we have adjusted the estimated sale amount in Form 3 while issuing this certificate. 
	The details regarding the KYC of customers, sale price, received amount, and unit numbers have been provided based on the information given by the promoter of the project. 
	This certificate has been issued based on the certified books of accounts provided by the promoters of the project.
